originalText.text: DO NOT COME HERE. I read the reviews and I decided to come here anyway. HUGE a mistake. It’s a scam. I bought a spot hero they wouldn’t honor it. Thankfully SpotHero understood and refunded me.  I could say so much more about how nasty the people downstairs were, but I think you get the point from reading the other reviews of this place. However the guys upstairs who valet your car were very nice. But that’s the only good thing I could find about this place. Huge scam don’t go.  If I could give zero stars I would.

originalText.text: Horrible park house. I reserved from 2-5 pm With SpotHero. Arrived shortly before 2 and parked. I then returned early from my appointment at 2:50. When I went in to get my car they told me I had to pay for the few minutes I was there early regardless of the fact that I was leaving over 2 hours before the end of my reservation freeing up their garage. The customer before me got the same exact scam. Take your business elsewhere.

originalText.text: Not sure about all the negative the reviews. Just another parking garage. Nothing nice or fancy just outdated elevator and concrete. But what else do you need? The proximity to the Lincoln tunnel makes it an easy pick for going into the city.

originalText.text: Garage is NOT open 24/7. No working time is posted anywhere. They close at 10pm in the city that never sleeps.. Unbelievable! Tried reporting this to corporate and gave up after 1 hr on hold.
